Bessemer Venture Partners: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 8:32 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Bessemer Venture Partners



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bessemer Venture Partners is a venture capital firm specializing in investments in seed stage, early stage, start-up companies, early venture, hyper-growth startups, late venture, emerging growth, and growth capital in the fintech sector. The firm also incubates companies. It seeks to invest in enterprise, consumer and healthcare technology companies. The firm invests in energy; utilities including electric power generation by nuclear fuels and fossil fuels, and water purification, clean technology; financial services such as banking and insurance; financial technology; healthcare including therapeutics, healthcare services, healthcare information technology, biotechnology, medical devices, ...
Bessemer Venture Partners is a venture capital firm specializing in investments in seed stage, early stage, start-up companies, early venture, hyper-growth startups, late venture, emerging growth, and growth capital in the fintech sector. The firm also incubates companies. It seeks to invest in enterprise, consumer and healthcare technology companies. The firm invests in energy; utilities including electric power generation by nuclear fuels and fossil fuels, and water purification, clean technology; financial services such as banking and insurance; financial technology; healthcare including therapeutics, healthcare services, healthcare information technology, biotechnology, medical devices, and diagnostics; applications, enterprise mobile; data security; cyber security; cloud computing; industry specific software, Internet; developer tools, machine intelligence, internet of things, intellectual property; online retail; software including enterprise software; emerging hardware and software technologies; Cloud/Software as a Service (SaaS); software-defined networking; internet advertising technology; consumer technologies including consumer Internet; digital and mobile media; life sciences; telecommunications; communications including communications technology; advanced web technologies; data storage including optical storage systems, networking, and semiconductors including memory chips. The firm also invests in agriculture; consumer spending, consumer services including analytics and education, information, mobile, marketplaces, video, social, commerce and services, entertainment, and power and infrastructure in India. It also invests in storage; services; data infrastructure, space technology, consumer web, software and appliances that increase the efficiency and performance of the existing enterprise and data center infrastructure; e-commerce and payments infrastructure for small and medium web businesses using service sales models; enterprise software and SaaS companies using low cost online marketing and sales models; platforms for online lead generation for on-line and off-line businesses; applications and solutions that leverage solid state disks and non-volatile memory; and solutions that provide for more granular and intelligent matching of online ads in Israel. The firm invests globally with a focus on Asia-Pacific including India; United States including North America; Latin America including Brazil; Israel; and Europe including Russia. It typically makes investments in the range of $.1 million and $75 million. The firm seeks to acquire a seat on the Board of Directors of the portfolio companies. Bessemer Venture Partners was founded in 1911 and is based in Menlo Park, California with additional offices across the United States and Asia.
Detailed Description


